name: General Icon Pack
description:
General Icon Pack is our first icon set here on Figma Community and we are super happy for this.


The set is made of 250 icons made to be consistent and to fit your website or app projects.


Every icon is made using a 1,5px stroke on a 24px grid.


We know the pack need more icons and we are welling to increase it, but for that we need you feedback and help. So, please ask for more icons in the comments section.


Follow us on our instagram to see what we are up to next.

https://www.instagram.com/handzon.design
